snippet.title: Emerald Shores - Announcement Trailer 2018 | PS4, PS Vita, PSTV, Steam (Windows, Linux)
snippet.description:
Out now on PS4, PS Vita, and Steam for $4.99!

https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/emerald-shores-ps4/
https://store.steampowered.com/app/970470/Emerald_Shores/

Website: http://www.fordesoft.com
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/fordesoft

Emerald Shores is a challenging, 90s-inspired run-and-jump 2D platformer. Level up as you progress through challenging levels, tough boss battles, minigames, sidequests, and secret unlockable levels, featuring an original soundtrack entirely composed by the developer, packed with 26 catchy tracks.
